| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3115 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7fa70647-1523-5886-8314-2adc7829d0a9"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
